@startuml form-import-sequence
actor "DevOps / Admin" as AD
participant "SCP CLI" as CLI
participant "Form Service" as FS
participant "Metadata Registry" as MR
participant "Audit System" as AS

AD -> CLI : Run `forms:import --file my-form.yaml`
CLI -> CLI : Validate YAML against Core Schema
CLI -> FS : Push Payload (Multipart/JSON)

FS -> FS : Verify Auth Token & Tenant Scope
FS -> MR : Check existing formKey Collision

alt New Form
  FS -> MR : Store as Version 1
else Update
  FS -> MR : Increment Version & Perform Diff
end

FS -> AS : Log FORM_IMPORT event
FS --> AD : Success (Version ID: 45)
@enduml
